# Targeted UI Upgrade — Safe Visual Improvements

Fix the "Win97" look without breaking any functionality. All changes are visual-only (ttk.Style, padding, colors) — no logic rewiring.

## Phase 1: Treeview Dark Theme (Highest Impact)

### [MODIFY] [projects_section.py](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/ui/projects_section.py)

Restyle the Projects Treeview:
- **Headers**: Dark bg `#1a1a2e` with subtle border-bottom, no 3D relief
- **Rows**: Alternating `#1e1e2e` / `#252538` for visual separation
- **Selected row**: Accent blue `#2563EB` instead of harsh system blue
- **Scrollbar**: Style ttk.Scrollbar to match dark theme (clam theme allows this)
- **Row height**: Increase from 26 → 30 for easier click targets

### [MODIFY] [product_tab.py](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/ui/product_tab.py)

Same Treeview restyling for the Objects panel.

