## Phase 2: Global Dark Scrollbar + Spacing

### [NEW] [ui/theme.py](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/ui/theme.py)

Create a shared theme module that:
- Defines all dark color constants in one place
- Provides `apply_dark_treeview_style()` function to style all ttk widgets
- Provides `apply_dark_scrollbar_style()` for consistent scrollbars

### [MODIFY] [main_window.py](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/ui/main_window.py)

- Call `apply_dark_treeview_style()` once at startup
- Slightly increase padding between major sections

