## Phase 3: Lag Fixes

### [MODIFY] [projects_section.py](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/ui/projects_section.py)

- Throttle [update_project()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/ui/projects_section.py#413-429) calls — batch UI updates instead of per-call refresh

### [MODIFY] [searchable_combo.py](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/ui/searchable_combo.py)

- Debounce filter keystrokes (150ms delay) to reduce widget churn
- Limit visible items to 15 max in dropdown

